OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJewish students want change
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter NUS antisemitism     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fclaims                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Amy Cregor, a drama student at the     
OL,6, University of Leeds, was on her way to 
OL,7, campus for a crunch-time rehearsal when
OL,8, she heard the antisemitic slur.        
OL,10,FThe next thing she knew, her hair and  
OL,11,Fclothes were covered with barbecue     
OL,12,Fsauce. Then her attackers drove away.  
OL,14,F"I was a bit in shock," she said. "I   
OL,15,Fhad a bit of a cry to myself, but I was
OL,16,Fjust like, 'Pull yourself together'."  
OL,18,FAmy had been wearing a Star of David   
OL,19,Fnecklace that day, which all four of   
OL,20,Fher grandparents had clubbed together  
OL,21,Fto buy her when she was a baby.        
